        	<h2>About WonderOps</h2>
             <div class="why-cho_inner_subtext"><img src="./images/hat-wand.jpg">

WonderOps services are focused on providing value added information security services to small businesses. As a small business ourself, we know what it is like to need to find competent support while managing costs. Our objective is simply to provide good IT services to our clients. 
<br><br>

Our company mantra "Performing IT Magic" is meant to convey our desire to relieve you of the burden of the details of IT and let us get you the results you need to operate your business. The team at WonderOps holds leading edge certifications in Amazon Web Services and Jenkins CI/CD tooling. We have experience in Linux and Windows system administration, Information Security, Enterprise Architecture, Configuration Management tools like Chef, Monitoring, Automation and ITSM. Our decades of experience in the IT industry means you can relax and rely on us to service all of your small business IT needs. 
